  "html": "<div class=\"mw-parser-output\"><div role=\"note\" class=\"hatnote navigation-not-searchable\" style=\"font-style: italic;padding-left: 1.6em;margin-bottom: 0.5em;\">For the companion of Princess Daella Targaryen, see <a href=\"/index.php/Simon_Staunton_(squire)\" title=\"Simon Staunton (squire)\">Simon Staunton (squire)</a>. For the unnamed character named \"Simon Staunton\" in <i>House of the Dragon</i>, see <a href=\"/index.php/Lord_Staunton\" title=\"Lord Staunton\">Lord Staunton</a>.</div>\n<table class=\"infobox\" style=\"min-width:22em;max-width:32em;border-collapse:separate;border-spacing:3px\"><tbody><tr><th colspan=\"2\" style=\"text-align:center;font-size:125%;font-weight:bold;font-weight:bold; background: none; line-height: 1.1em;\"><table style=\"width:100%\"><tbody><tr><td style=\"border:none;vertical-align:top;text-align:left;width:50px\"><a href=\"/index.php/House_Staunton\" title=\"House Staunton\"><img alt=\"House Staunton.svg\" src=\"/images/thumb/9/9e/House_Staunton.svg/50px-House_Staunton.svg.png\" width=\"50\" height=\"55\" srcset=\"/images/thumb/9/9e/House_Staunton.svg/75px-House_Staunton.svg.png 1.5x, /images/thumb/9/9e/House_Staunton.svg/100px-House_Staunton.svg.png 2x\" /></a></td><td style=\"border:none;vertical-align:middle;text-align:center;padding:0px 7px 5px 7px\"><span style=\"font-size:80%;font-weight:normal\"> Ser</span><br />Simon Staunton</td><td style=\"border:none;vertical-align:top;text-align:right;width:50px\"><a href=\"/index.php/House_Staunton\" title=\"House Staunton\"><img alt=\"House Staunton.svg\" src=\"/images/thumb/9/9e/House_Staunton.svg/50px-House_Staunton.svg.png\" width=\"50\" height=\"55\" srcset=\"/images/thumb/9/9e/House_Staunton.svg/75px-House_Staunton.svg.png 1.5x, /images/thumb/9/9e/House_Staunton.svg/100px-House_Staunton.svg.png 2x\" /></a></td></tr></tbody></table></th></tr><tr><td colspan=\"2\" class=\"infobox-image\" style=\"text-align:center\">\n<a href=\"/index.php/File:Simon_Staunton_by_Lopata_4.jpg\" class=\"image\"><img alt=\"Simon Staunton by Lopata 4.jpg\" src=\"/images/thumb/2/24/Simon_Staunton_by_Lopata_4.jpg/350px-Simon_Staunton_by_Lopata_4.jpg\" width=\"350\" height=\"348\" srcset=\"/images/thumb/2/24/Simon_Staunton_by_Lopata_4.jpg/525px-Simon_Staunton_by_Lopata_4.jpg 1.5x, /images/thumb/2/24/Simon_Staunton_by_Lopata_4.jpg/700px-Simon_Staunton_by_Lopata_4.jpg 2x\" /></a><div>Simon by Lopata Four</div></td></tr><tr><td colspan=\"2\" style=\"text-align:center\">\n<hr /></td></tr><tr><th scope=\"row\">Title</th><td>\n<a href=\"/index.php/Knight\" title=\"Knight\">Ser</a></td></tr><tr><th scope=\"row\">Allegiance</th><td>\n<a href=\"/index.php/House_Staunton\" title=\"House Staunton\">House Staunton</a></td></tr><tr><th scope=\"row\">Culture</th><td>\n<a href=\"/index.php/Crownlands\" title=\"Crownlands\">Crownlands</a></td></tr><tr><th scope=\"row\">Born</th><td>\n<a href=\"/index.php/Rook%27s_Rest\" title=\"Rook&#39;s Rest\">Rook's Rest</a><sup id=\"cite_ref-Rawoiafsimon_staunton.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_1-0\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Rawoiafsimon_staunton.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-1\">&#91;1&#93;</a></sup></td></tr><tr><th scope=\"row\">Spouse</th><td>\nLady <a href=\"/index.php/Rohanne_Webber\" title=\"Rohanne Webber\">Rohanne Webber</a></td></tr><tr><th scope=\"row\">Issue</th><td>\nDaughter (possibly)<sup id=\"cite_ref-Issue_2-0\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Issue-2\">&#91;N 1&#93;</a></sup></td></tr><tr><th scope=\"row\">Book</th><td>\n<i><a href=\"/index.php/The_Sworn_Sword\" title=\"The Sworn Sword\">The Sworn Sword</a></i> (mentioned)</td></tr></tbody></table>\n<p><b>Simon Staunton</b> was a <a href=\"/index.php/Knight\" title=\"Knight\">knight</a> from <a href=\"/index.php/House_Staunton\" title=\"House Staunton\">House Staunton</a>. He was married to Lady <a href=\"/index.php/Rohanne_Webber\" title=\"Rohanne Webber\">Rohanne Webber</a> becoming her third husband. His brother was <a href=\"/index.php/Septon\" title=\"Septon\">Septon</a> <a href=\"/index.php/Sefton_Staunton\" title=\"Sefton Staunton\">Sefton</a>.\n</p>\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"Histoy\">Histoy</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Simon_Staunton&amp;action=edit&amp;section=1\" class=\"tw-editsection-onhover\" title=\"Edit section: Histoy\"><span class=\"glyphicon glyphicon-pencil\"></span> </a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h2>\n<p>Simon died choking on a chicken bone.<sup id=\"cite_ref-Rtss.7B.7B.7B2.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_3-0\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Rtss.7B.7B.7B2.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-3\">&#91;2&#93;</a></sup>\n</p>\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"Notes\">Notes</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Simon_Staunton&amp;action=edit&amp;section=2\" class=\"tw-editsection-onhover\" title=\"Edit section: Notes\"><span class=\"glyphicon glyphicon-pencil\"></span> </a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h2>\n<div class=\"references-small\">\n<div class=\"mw-references-wrap\"><ol class=\"references\">\n<li id=\"cite_note-Issue-2\"><span class=\"mw-cite-backlink\"><a href=\"#cite_ref-Issue_2-0\">↑</a></span> <span class=\"reference-text\">It is currently unknown if <a href=\"/index.php/Rohanne_Webber\" title=\"Rohanne Webber\">Rohanne Webber</a>'s daughter is by Simon, her third husband, or <a href=\"/index.php/Rolland_Uffering\" title=\"Rolland Uffering\">Rolland Uffering</a>, her fourth.</span>\n</li>\n</ol></div></div>\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"References\">References</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Simon_Staunton&amp;action=edit&amp;section=3\" class=\"tw-editsection-onhover\" title=\"Edit section: References\"><span clas